This is a demo Scala + Play + Redis application
===============================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `activator dist`.
Require:
- SBT 0.13.x
- Scala 2.11.4
- Play - newest version
- Redis 2.8.4
Usage:
1. ./activator clean compile ~run 
or with remote debug enabled: ./activator -jvm-debug <your-port-number> clean compile ~run
2. Once done, access application web URL: http://localhost:9000
3. Connect to websocket through clicking re-connect
4. Input new user name and age then submit the form.
   new user will be added to DB and appear on the list of user on the screen.
   
   Known Bug:
   Message sending from client is not compatible with server validation. 
